  "title": "Project  Coordinator",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Responsible for site activities, coordination and supervision works related to engineering and systems design.</li><li>Coordinate with clients, architects, sub-contractors, and other relevant authorities Plan and ensure M&E works are completed in line with Master Programme and micro-schedule.</li><li>Coordination with our scaffolding subcontractors and ensure their work to comply with PE approved drawing and issue PE cos promptly.</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Architecture / Civil Engineering</li><li>At least 2 year (s) of relevant working experience in site coordination work</li><li>Possess Building Construction Safety Supervisor and Working-at-heights Supervisor certificate</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li></ul><p>Willing to travel to Tuas South. (pick up transport at Tuas MRT)</p><p>If you meet the above requirements, please send your resume to my email.cindyhan@sinohydro.com.sg Thanks.</p>",
